<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_151" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_151_r1l20">Coſtencʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_151_r1l21"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als vvir euch nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> / vnd gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l22">vns cʒuvviſſen laſſen / von den <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd leuffen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Aller - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l23">gnedigiſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Römiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künigs etc 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l24">daʒ Jr vns beẏ dem gegenvvertigen poten ſo Jr eygentlıchſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l25">mügt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vviſſen laſſen wöllet / vvie eʒ <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l26">darümb gelegen 
<del rend="strikethrough">oder </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_151_line_1573112521503_322">vnd </ab></add> geſtalt ſeẏ / oder ob Jr ſıder icht newer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l27">oder fremder leuffe oder ſache erfaren oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> habt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_151_line_1573112532058_329">het </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l28"><expan>Alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit das füglich ſeẏ / Daran beweiſt Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l29">beſunder lieb vnd <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> / dıe vvir Jn <expan>ſölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l30"><expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vmb ewr <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> begern <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>cʒuverd<ex>ienen</ex></expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_151" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Costencz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als wir euch nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und gebeten
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> uns czu wissen lassen von den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und leuffen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> allergnedigisten
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        künigs, etc., also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns bey dem
                        gegenwertigen poten, so ir eygentlichst mügt,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen lassen wöllet,
                        wie ez <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> noch darümb gelegen <add>und</add>
                        gestalt sey oder ob ir sider icht newer oder fremder leuffe oder sache
                        erfaren oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>het</add>, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit das füglich sey. Daran beweist ir uns
                        besunder lieb und <expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>, die wir in
                                <expan>sölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> umb ewr <expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan>
                        begern, <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>czu verd<ex>ienen</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
